References
Seeker by Leon Cmielewski – Inspired me to include projected or animated visual effects that emphasize movement and make the clock feel more dynamic.
Google Material Design – I like its clean layout, readable typography, and simple user interface. I plan to use these design principles to make the clock easy to understand while keeping the focus on the animation and movement.
